body: Is there anything in marketplace for ZAP add-ons that rely on Filters? If so and those add-ons have been abandoned but are still being used, that may be a reason to defer this decision a bit longer.

No there isnt. If there was we could still change them to use one of the alternative options.
Filters are relic from Paros days that we've never really used in the ZAP code base.
